affymetrix.calvin.utils
Class AffymetrixGuidType

java.lang.Object
  affymetrix.calvin.utils.AffymetrixGuidType

public class AffymetrixGuidType
extends java.lang.Object

Provides a type for the Affy GUID. Affymetrix software requires GUIDs to be unique. In order to provide maximum flexibility for users our software, Affymetrix does not require GUIDs to be RFC 4122 compliant. The GUIDs generated by the generateGuid function in the Java SDJ are RFC 4122 compliant. *
